{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is equal to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"text":", viewport","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"properties such as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"text":" assume a viewport that matches the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map center is effectively shifted downward.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"type":"text","text":" property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the value of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property may be overridden at any time."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The usage of "},{"code":"automa